Autenticaci√≥n:

Crear Servicio:

curl -i -X POST \--url http://172.21.0.3:8001:8001/services/ \--data 'name=HELADERIA' \--data 'url=http://localhost:9001'

Instalar pluguin en el servicio:

curl -X POST http://172.21.0.3:8001/services/HELADERIA/plugins \
    --data "name=basic-auth"  \
    --data "config.hide_credentials=true"

Crear Usuario:

curl -d "username=unaitxo&custom_id=GALLETA" http://172.21.0.3:8001/consumers/

curl -X POST http://172.21.0.3:8001/consumers/unaitxo/basic-auth \
    --data "username=unaitxo" \
    --data "password=unaitxin"
